    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride and it's looking for a great new home. It\u2019s been well-loved and is in really solid shape, making it the perfect companion for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. Everything runs just like it should, and it's super clean and ready to hit the road today! If you're looking for a dependable car that still has tons of life left in it, this is the one for you. Drop me a message if you'd like to take it for a spin!",
