    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example featuring the S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. The dual-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe\u2014a known weak point\u2014has been reinforced with plates to ensure chassis rigidity. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery through the corners. The suspension has been upgraded with adjustable coilovers and polyurethane bushings, sharpening the turn-in response while maintaining the car's balanced 50/50 weight distribution. Recent maintenance includes a valve adjustment and rod bearing inspection, confirming this vehicle is track-ready and mechanically robust.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Mechanically sound. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear. Ready for immediate sale.",
