    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s still got so much life left in it? This car has been such a joy to own and is in really solid shape. It\u2019s been well-loved, kept clean, and drives like a total dream! It\u2019s the perfect companion for daily commutes or weekend getaways. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself how great it handles. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
