    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This chassis has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings to maintain optimal suspension geometry under lateral load. Power is delivered to the rear wheels through a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. While the exterior shows minor road patina, the drivetrain remains robust, offering the linear power delivery and 8,000 RPM redline these M-cars are known for. A prime candidate for an enthusiast seeking a driver-quality legend with documented mechanical upkeep.",
